abstract.text: An object that encapsualtes the performance metrics collected by the URL Loading System during the execution of a session task.
An object that encapsualtes the performance metrics collected by the URL Loading System during the execution of a session task.

media-3162616.alt: Diagram showing the temporal metrics for a URL session task. When a task starts, it performs a DNS lookup and then starts a connection. If the connection is encrypted, the user agent starts a TLS security handshake to secure the connection. After the connection to the server is established, the user agent requests the specified resource, and receives a response.
